{
  "stem": "5275.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She got a birth certificate for me under the name of Stephen Halicki, H-A-L-I-C-K-I, polish name, born in Lida, L-I-D-A, which, at that time, was in the part of Poland occupied by Russia.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So she thought that the Germans would never be able to find that this was false paper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She gave me that paper, and she told me to leave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a bunch of-- what do you call them?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Groups of-- of Jews that were leaving the ghetto each day under supervision of the Wehrmacht, I think, to do some work outside for them-- digging something, or doing something, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one day-- it was July, I believe, 12, 1942-- I put on myself several pairs of underwear, several pants, several shirts, several sweaters, several jackets.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was dying inside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was middle of the summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She gave me those false papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father told me to go to a friend of his who-- gave me the address out in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he told me to go to our maid in Checiny, C-H-E-C-I-N-Y, which was in southern Poland where she lived, and maybe hide there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Natalcia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "N-A-T-A-L-C-I-A.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went with this-- oh, so my father [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [EMOTIONAL] [DRINKS WATER] met us at the exit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [EMOTIONAL] [QUIETLY] I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS WATER] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I tell ?] my mother-- [TEARFUL] I'm-- [COUGHS] I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I will never see him again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SOBS] And I left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[BLOWS NOSE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to those people in Warsaw, who told me that they were too afraid to keep me, so I had to leave.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to this group of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on one of the streets, the big boulevard, I-- I-- I-- my mother told me what do.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
